Package edu.ncsu.csc216.stp.model.test_plans

Class TestPlan

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.stp.model.test_plans.AbstractTestPlan
edu.ncsu.csc216.stp.model.test_plans.TestPlan
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<TestPlan>
public class TestPlan extends AbstractTestPlan implements Comparable<TestPlan>
The TestPlan class manages a list of TestCases, adding them, returning them, and comparing them. It also extends AbstractTestPlan and so inherits its functionality.
Author:
Jeremiah Knizley, Ryan McPhee

    • compareTo

      public int compareTo(TestPlan s)
      Compares the names of two TestPlans, the comparison is case sensitive.
      Specified by:
      compareTo in interface Comparable<TestPlan>
      Parameters:
      s - the TestPlan to be compared to
      Returns:
      int depending on the comparison. If this TestPlan is less than (Alphabetically) then TestPlan s, a -1 is returned. If they are equal, 0. If this TestPlan is greater, a 1 is returned.
